### Variables
@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000/api
@token = your_token_here

### ============================================
### PUBLIC ENDPOINTS (No Token Required)
### ============================================

### 1. Register New User
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Test User",
    "email": "testuser@example.com",
    "password": "password123",
    "password_confirmation": "password123",
    "phone": "081234567890",
    "company_name": "Test Company"
}

### 2. Login - COPY TOKEN from response!
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "testuser@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### ============================================
### PROTECTED ENDPOINTS (Need Token)
### ============================================
### NOTE: Replace @token value above with token from login response!

### 3. Get Current User Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/user
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 4. Update Profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Updated Name",
    "phone": "081234567890",
    "company_name": "Updated Company"
}

### 5. Dashboard Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 6. Get All Invoices
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 7. Get Invoice Detail (change ID as needed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoices/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 8. Get All Payments
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 9. Get Payment Detail (change ID as needed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 10. Get All Quotations
GET {{baseUrl}}/quotations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 11. Get Quotation Detail (change ID as needed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/quotations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 12. Approve Quotation
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotations/1/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 13. Reject Quotation
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotations/1/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "rejection_reason": "Harga terlalu mahal"
}

### 14. Get All Items
GET {{baseUrl}}/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 15. Get Low Stock Items
GET {{baseUrl}}/items/status/low-stock
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 16. Get All Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 17. Mark Notification as Read
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notifications/1/read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 18. Mark All Notifications as Read
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 19. Get All Project Requests
GET {{baseUrl}}/project-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 20. Get Project Request Detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/project-requests/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 21. Create New Project Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/project-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Website Development",
    "description": "Need a corporate website",
    "type": "web_development",
    "budget": 50000000,
    "deadline": "2026-02-28"
}

### 22. Debug Quotations (Troubleshooting)
GET {{baseUrl}}/debug/quotations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 23. Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
